text: Frédéric Boeni (born 15 November 1913, date of death unknown) was a Swiss diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Swiss male divers Category:Olympic divers of Switzerland Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
